Class GenerationQR

  • java.lang.Object
    • GenerationQR

  • public class GenerationQR
extends java.lang.Object
    class that generates a QR code, which contains a value from a line of an input file (example .qrdata) between the first and second spaces (in this case LPA link to download the eSIM profile). One QR code corresponds to each line.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ivan Emelyanenko
